---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Agency Services — Meridian" description="Bespoke SEO partnership with direct access to Jeremy. A done-with-you service where strategy, execution, and results are handled personally. Limited client slots available.">

  <!-- Self-Serve Banner -->
  <div class="bg-dark-card border-b border-dark-border py-3 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm text-body-muted">
      Prefer to <strong class="text-accent">run your own SEO</strong> with our AI platform? 
      <a href="/pricing" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">View self-serve plans ($49–$199/mo) →</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center bg-gradient-to-b from-dark to-dark-card">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-32 pb-20">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent mb-6">Done With You</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-hero-text leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-4xl">
        The strategy is bespoke.<br />The execution is
        <span class="text-accent">hands-on.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-body-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Not every business wants to run their own SEO. Some need a partner who treats their search presence like their own. That's what this is: direct access, bespoke strategy, and execution handled personally by someone who measures everything.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Book an intro call
        </a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-4 border border-dark-border text-body-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/20 font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          See how it works
        </a>
      </div>
      <!-- Social Proof Teaser -->
      <div class="mt-16 flex items-center gap-6">
        <div class="flex -space-x-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/20 border-2 border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-accent">IS</div>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/30 border-2 border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-accent">RS</div>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/40 border-2 border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-accent">+</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-body-muted">Trusted by security firms, financial services companies, and a small roster of growing businesses.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Limited Slots -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-dark leading-tight">Small by design.</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-light-text text-lg leading-relaxed">
            We work with a <strong class="text-dark">limited number of clients at a time</strong> — not because we can't scale, but because this work requires attention that doesn't batch well. When you sign on, you get:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent text-sm font-bold">1</span>
              <span class="text-light-text"><strong class="text-dark">Direct access to Jeremy</strong> — no account managers, no junior staff, no handoffs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent text-sm font-bold">2</span>
              <span class="text-light-text"><strong class="text-dark">Strategy built for your business</strong> — not a template, not a playbook, but research into your market, competitors, and opportunities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              <span class="text-light-text"><strong class="text-dark">Content in your voice</strong> — every draft is written specifically for you, not spun from prompts</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent text-sm font-bold">4</span>
              <span class="text-light-text"><strong class="text-dark">Full transparency</strong> — you see exactly what the platform is doing, what we're prioritizing, and why</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-hero-text rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <blockquote class="text-light-text italic text-lg leading-relaxed">
            "Jeremy doesn't just send reports. He understands our business, our competitive landscape, and what actually moves the needle. It's like having a senior SEO director who actually does the work."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center text-dark font-bold">JS</div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-dark">Client, Security Industry</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-light-text">Partnership since 2024</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="bg-hero-text py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-dark leading-tight">How the partnership works</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-light-text text-lg">The platform handles the volume. I handle the judgment, strategy, and quality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-16">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">Week 1</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mt-2 mb-4">Deep Dive & Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">
              We start with a comprehensive audit of your current state — not just technical SEO, but your competitive positioning, content gaps, and keyword opportunities. I build a 90-day strategy specific to your business, your resources, and your growth goals.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Full technical audit & GSC analysis</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Competitor gap analysis</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Keyword strategy & priority matrix</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Brand voice documentation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-dark">Technical Audit Report</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-dark">Competitor Analysis Deck</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-dark">90-Day Strategy Document</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-dark">Brand Voice Guidelines</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="md:order-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">Every Week</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mt-2 mb-4">Continuous Execution</h3>
            <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">
              The platform runs daily — audits, monitoring, content intelligence. I review everything, prioritize what matters, and deliver publish-ready work. You get a weekly report with clear next steps, and I'm available for questions or strategy adjustments as things change.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Daily technical monitoring & issue flagging</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> 2+ SEO content drafts per week (your voice)</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Weekly content intelligence brief</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Friday performance report with WoW trends</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="md:order-1 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Monday</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-dark">Content intelligence scan completed — trending topics identified for your industry</p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Wednesday</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-dark">2 content drafts delivered — blog post + landing page optimization</p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Friday</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-dark">Weekly performance report + strategy notes</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">Every Month</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mt-2 mb-4">Strategic Review</h3>
            <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">
              We look at what moved, what didn't, and why. I prepare a strategy deck covering month-over-month performance, competitive shifts, and next month's priorities. This is where we adjust course based on data, not hunches.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Month-over-month performance analysis</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Competitor movement tracking</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> Updated keyword strategy</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> 60-minute strategy call</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent">+47%</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-light-text">Organic traffic growth (average client, 6 months)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-light-text">Indexed pages</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-dark">+23%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-light-text">Avg. position</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-dark">+4.2 spots</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-light-text">Click-through rate</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-dark">+18%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
                <span class="text-light-text">Content published</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-dark">8-10 pieces/mo</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Tiers -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-dark leading-tight">Choose your level of partnership</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-light-text text-lg">All tiers include direct access to Jeremy and our full platform infrastructure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Foundation -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark">Foundation</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-2">$750<span class="text-lg font-normal text-light-text">/mo</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-light-text text-sm">Best for: businesses that create their own content but need professional technical oversight and strategic guidance.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Daily GSC + rank tracking pull (up to 20 keywords)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Live page metadata audit (title, meta, H1, canonical, schema)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Core Web Vitals monitoring</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Technical issues ranked by impact</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Weekly performance report</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Monthly strategy review</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Growth -->
        <div class="relative border-2 border-accent rounded-2xl p-8">
          <span class="absolute -top-3 left-8 bg-accent text-white text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most Popular</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark">Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-2">$1,500<span class="text-lg font-normal text-light-text">/mo</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-light-text text-sm">Best for: businesses ready to scale organic content production with a dedicated partner.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Everything in Foundation</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Copy-paste technical fixes delivered</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">2 SEO content drafts per week (your voice)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Weekly content intelligence brief</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Friday client-ready email draft</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Up to 30 keywords tracked</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Weekly link prospecting</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Authority -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark">Authority</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-2">$2,500<span class="text-lg font-normal text-light-text">/mo</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-light-text text-sm">Best for: competitive markets where content velocity, strategic depth, and full-service execution matter.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Everything in Growth</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Competitor gap analysis</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Monthly strategy deck</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Content brief reviews and edits</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Unlimited keyword tracking</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Optional publish-on-behalf</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <p class="text-dark text-sm">Priority turnaround & support</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center mt-12 text-light-text">
        Not sure which tier fits? <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-medium transition-colors">Let's talk.</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Jeremy -->
  <section class="bg-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent mb-6">Your Partner</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">Built by someone who measures everything.</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body-muted leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Most SEO agencies treat organic search as a creative problem. I treat it as a data engineering problem.
            </p>
            <p>
              I built Meridian because I was tired of watching businesses pay for monthly reports that didn't move the needle. So I built the infrastructure first — automated audits, rank tracking, content pipelines, performance snapshots — and let the data drive the strategy.
            </p>
            <p>
              The result is an SEO operation that runs continuously, surfaces real opportunities, and creates content that's actually informed by what people are searching for this week — not what ranked two years ago.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-6">
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">15+</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-body-muted">Years in data engineering & SEO</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">47%</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-body-muted">Avg. organic traffic growth</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">&lt;10</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-body-muted">Active clients at a time</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-hero-text mb-6">Principles</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-hero-text mb-1">Show your work</h4>
              <p class="text-body-muted text-sm">Every recommendation comes with the data behind it. I don't ask you to trust me. I show you the numbers.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-hero-text mb-1">Continuous beats periodic</h4>
              <p class="text-body-muted text-sm">Monthly reporting is a relic. Your site is getting crawled every day. Your monitoring should match that pace.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-hero-text mb-1">Small by choice</h4>
              <p class="text-body-muted text-sm">I limit client count deliberately. Not because I can't scale, but because bespoke work requires actual attention.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="bg-hero-text py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-dark leading-tight mb-12">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">Who will I be working with?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Me, directly. I'm Jeremy, the founder. When you sign on for agency services, I'm the one building your strategy, reviewing your audits, and writing (or editing) your content. There are no junior account managers.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">How is this different from the self-serve platform?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">The self-serve platform gives you access to all our tools — you run your own SEO program. Agency services means I run it for you: bespoke strategy, content written specifically for your business, and direct access for questions and adjustments.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">Do I publish the content myself?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">By default, yes — you get publish-ready drafts with exact CMS instructions. For Authority tier clients, I can optionally publish directly to your site if you provide CMS access.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">How fast can we start?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Usually within one week of kickoff. I need to understand your business, build your brand voice document, and set up your tracking before we start producing content.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">Is there a contract?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Month-to-month. SEO takes time to compound, but I'd rather earn the renewal than lock you in. Most clients stay because the data shows it working, not because they have to.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">What happens if rankings drop?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">I catch it before you do — conversion decay monitoring and rank tracking fire daily. When something drops, you'll know why (algorithm update, new competitor content, technical regression) and you'll get a specific fix, not a vague explanation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark-card py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">Ready to talk?</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-muted text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">No pitch deck. Just an honest conversation about where you are, what you're trying to grow, and whether we're a good fit.</p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Book an intro call
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border border-dark-border text-body-muted hover:text-white hover:border-white/20 font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Compare with self-serve
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
